{"title":"已解决-Hexo Fluid主题本地搜索无法正常使用bug复现","uid":"b7299ee111bc51c458f38e9a92cd9083","slug":"bug_solve","date":"2023-12-12T06:17:43.000Z","updated":"2023-12-24T08:29:15.643Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/bug_solve.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121420578.webp","content":"<h1 id=\"已解决-Hexo-Fluid主题本地搜索无法正常使用bug复现\"><a href=\"#已解决-Hexo-Fluid主题本地搜索无法正常使用bug复现\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"[已解决]Hexo Fluid主题本地搜索无法正常使用bug复现\"></a>[已解决]Hexo Fluid主题本地搜索无法正常使用bug复现</h1><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>很好，通过发布这篇文章，我有发现了，yaml语法里面不能有<code>[]</code>，要不然hexo g的时候会报错，哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈，好你的</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"一、本地搜索无法使用\"><a href=\"#一、本地搜索无法使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、本地搜索无法使用\"></a>一、本地搜索无法使用</h2><p>如图，一直在转圈圈</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121409748.png\" alt=\"image-20231212140912128\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-1-F12查看\"><a href=\"#1-1-F12查看\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.1 F12查看\"></a>1.1 F12查看</h3><p><strong>发现状态为200，那么恭喜你，参考下文即可顺利解决问题</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121410703.png\" alt=\"image-20231212141000256\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-2-访问search-xml\"><a href=\"#1-2-访问search-xml\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.2 访问search.xml\"></a>1.2 访问search.xml</h3><p>显示这里，说明文章里面有些字符，无法识别</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121410237.png\" alt=\"image-20231212141045168\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-3-找到问题文章\"><a href=\"#1-3-找到问题文章\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.3 找到问题文章\"></a>1.3 找到问题文章</h3><p>网页拉倒最下面，确定文章关键字，如果文章数量太多，无法人为找到，本地打开search.xml文件</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121412383.png\" alt=\"image-20231212141205290\"></p>\n<p>本地搜索后，可以确定问题文章</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121413461.png\" alt=\"image-20231212141330341\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-4-解决字符问题\"><a href=\"#1-4-解决字符问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.4 解决字符问题\"></a>1.4 解决字符问题</h3><p>根据文件检索，定位。最终确定问题出现在这里</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121414635.png\" alt=\"image-20231212141423496\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p>放入代码块范围</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121415703.png\" alt=\"image-20231212141509628\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-5-大功告成\"><a href=\"#1-5-大功告成\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.5 大功告成\"></a>1.5 大功告成</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121415324.png\" alt=\"image-20231212141533804\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-6-重新部署发布即可\"><a href=\"#1-6-重新部署发布即可\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.6 重新部署发布即可\"></a>1.6 重新部署发布即可</h3><p>在网页端，也能正常检索了</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312121418506.png\" alt=\"image-20231212141811745\"></p>\n","text":"已解决-Hexo Fluid主题本地搜索无法正常使用bug复现...","permalink":"/post/bug_solve","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":354,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Hexo.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B7%B2%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3-Hexo-Fluid%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8bug%E5%A4%8D%E7%8E%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">[已解决]Hexo Fluid主题本地搜索无法正常使用bug复现</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">一、本地搜索无法使用</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-1-F12%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.1 F12查看</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-2-%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AEsearch-xml\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.2 访问search.xml</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-3-%E6%89%BE%E5%88%B0%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.3 找到问题文章</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-4-%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98\"